'''Docking bay 789012634''' was a [[Hangar/Legends|docking bay]] located on [[level 3301]] of [[Byblos/Legends|Byblos]] [[Byblos Starport Tower 214|tower 214]]. Some time during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], the [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] [[Crimson]] was arrested here by [[Imperial Office of Customs/Legends|Imperial Customs]]. Shortly after her arrest, she managed to escape with the help of her [[Protocol droid/Legends|protocol droid]] [[U-THR]] and drama once more took place in the docking bay, as she and the [[Droid/Legends|droid]] sabotaged the [[Blast door/Legends|blast doors]] and made off in the ''[[Starlight Red]]''.

